{"type": "article", "id": 20502, "title": "钢丝绳灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-11T07:24:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153040VRxjsfghOD3imrlP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tRF Objects 是荷兰设计师 Ralf Frickel 创立的工作室，擅长用钢丝绳制作有艺术感的灯饰。这两组灯饰分别致敬 20 世纪巴黎的钟形帽（Cloche hat）和 1920 年代的复古灯罩，钢丝绳有一定亮度，经过扭曲缠绕后捆绑在一起，保持着蓬松自然的状态。光源在中心，能投射出缠绕的阴影，很适合现代风格的室内。<a href=\"http://rfobjects.com/collection\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153037FXrtjGZ8vBbPuK6p.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061530373yePSdtpqK7Lcjl1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153038yWDmqZuehN90CKfB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153039DwU4ZAXNY2S5rpTL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}